size=1> Alysia glanced around the village sniffing where she could trying ton get a scent. And when she finally did she growled lowly. <br>
<br>
Aeceus and Arixa caugh the scent as well and Aeceus turned to the other two wolves.<br>
&quot;We should attack now and kill them all.&quot;<br>
<br>
Arixa blinked and looked to him.<br>
&quot;We have our orders Aeceus, we can't danger Hippolyte's life more than it is.&quot;<br>
<br>
Alysia nodded.<br>
&quot;Scan the village more so, put two wolves secretly guardingt every hut. Put five along the back line of the weaponry hut. Send Scythe to watch over the hut they keep Hippolyte in.&quot;<br>
<br>
Aeceus nodded and turned his back letting out a small simple bark to the others, keeping weary of any human near by. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=queenhera>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 236<br> <font color=#993300>(4/19/03 11:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=162>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/lilhera.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> tests</span><hr size=1> The sound of Hera's laugh echoed thru only Solari's head.  The Goddess did not want to disturb Elektra's sacrifice, nor disturb the other amazons.<br>
<br>
&quot;Solari, do you believe you are the only one fighting this battle?  Yes, you are leading them.  But, as their strength is led thru you...it is given by the Gods.  This sacrific is must be made in recognition of this fact.  Don't forget the Gods, Solari.  That would be a fool choice.&quot; <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 847<br> <font color=#993300>(4/19/03 11:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=163>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wolves Eyes</span><hr size=1> The roman captor began to rip at Hippolyte's clothing.  His purpose was sure to rape her.  And Hippolyte knew it.  She began to struggle even harder at her binds as he laughed. &quot;Yes, that's it struggle as I take you.  Weak woman you are not match.&quot;<br>
<br>
But, outside one of the lookouts quickly noticed the some of the wolves that had begun to surround the village.  And word got out quickly.  A man ran into the hut of the captor yelling, &quot;Marxus, there are wolves in the village.  Those beasts of the forests are sending their kind!&quot;<br>
<br>
Now she knew his name and would not forget it.  This man would die.  She would be sure of it and watch.  <br>
<br>
Marxus turned around facing the man who entered.  &quot;Come man, don't tell me a couple wolves have you scared.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;But, Marxus...it is more then a couple wolves.&quot;  Just as he spoke they could hear one of the few dogs of the village getting into a fight with one of the wolves.<br>
<br>
Marxus cursed, &quot;Go, I will be out in a minute.&quot;  The man ran out and Marxus turned to his captive.  &quot;Don't worry, I will be back.&quot; He then send the back of his hand across her cheek.  &quot;And that is for thinking of ways to get loose.&quot;<br>
<br>
Hipps head was knocked hard into the post again, and then she turned to face him again.  Watching him leave the hut, she now could taste the blood on her lips again.  <br>
<br>
Looking up at the top of the roof, she let a tear fall finally from one corner of an eye.  &quot;Hera, have you left me?&quot; <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

