Solari grabbed her cloak from her bag and placed it over her as she walked out to greet Mel. <br>
 &quot;Come inside and get out of this rain child.&quot; Solari said soothingly. &quot;Hipp will kill me if you catch a cold.&quot; Solari's uncanny sense of feeling told her that Mel was upset and had been crying. She felt her emotion with a great deal of compassion and took her into her arms, giving her a reassuring hug that things would be ok. <br>
 &quot;Would you like anything to eat or drink? There isnt much here, but i do have a few things in my bag.&quot; She asked softly as they made their way back into the shelter where Solari had been.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=odessaofpaphos>Odessa of Paphos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 211<br> <font color=#993300>(4/24/03 4:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=172>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/xvmegvxwpt/images/amarice_11.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enter Melanippe Hipp's sister</span><hr size=1> She came back to Solari after praying, wet and cold; but it didn't seem to bother the Scynthian Queen of Paphos. She bowed in respect to Melanippe.<br>
